	<h1 style="font-family: Lobster Two">La numbri (The numbers)</h1>
	<div class="ui fitted divider"></div>
	<p>Idos numeral system is super simple! It was designed to be able to be put together easy, with out the chance to mess up! When you start pronouncing bigger numbers (up in the thousands, millions) you will notice that it all goes with a good flow, and there is no rocks to fall over! Now, because of that; they may seem short, but when you start using them you will notice how easy it is to count in Ido!</p>
